  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Moto Roader is a futuristic racing game that allows up to five players to compete against each other. Players use the cash earned when they win a race to power up their machine. Not only can they change the \"tire\" and \"body\" of their vehicles, but they also can add \"special\" parts. Jump over tall obstacles with a \"hopper\" and blast past rivals at incredible speeds with \"nitro.\" What multiplayer game would be complete without attack items? Use a forward-launching \"grenade\" or a backward-dropping \"bomber\" to blow up and knock away rivals. Outmaneuver rivals in all eight heats to become the champion.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
